<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.8.6">
<l>vaṭivāy maḻuvē paṭaiyāka vantu tōṉṟi mūveḻukāl</l>
<l>paṭiyā raracu kaḷaikaṭṭa pāḻi yāṉai yammāṉai</l>
<l>kuṭiyā vaṇṭu koṇṭuṇṇak kōla nīlam maṭṭukukkum</l>
<l>kaṭiyār puṟavil kaṇṇapurat taṭiyēṉ kaṇṭu koṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord, the mighty one who weeded out</l>
<l rend="indent">the kings who filled the earth</l>
<l>Three-times-seven times, coming and appearing</l>
<l rend="indent">with a sharp-edged axe as a weapon,</l>
<l>I, his servant, saw for myself in Kaṇṇapuram in a fragrance-filled land</l>
<l>Where nectar spills from beautiful blue lilies</l>
<l rend="indent">as bees in swarms take and sip [it].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
